{
  "texts": [
    "Loveleen et al. [109] discuss AD prediction using tree-based models.",
    "The study employed machine learning algorithms like LR, SVM, KNN, Multilayer Perceptron, and decision trees to classify patients into demented and non-demented groups.",
    "The authors introduced an explanation-driven Human-Computer Interaction (HCI) model, achieving high accuracy across algorithms and comparing performance with state-of-the-art deep learning models.",
    "To enhance interpretability, LIME and SHAP explanation algorithms were applied to black-box deep learning models.",
    "Rashmi et al. [110] diagnoses AD with various datasets and emphasises the importance of explainability beyond diagnosis."
  ]
}